267
00:27:44,914 --> 00:27:47,458
- I need at least a week...
- Okay!

268
00:27:54,256 --> 00:27:59,095
Put the radio on the dash
and your hands on the wheel.

269
00:28:18,614 --> 00:28:20,866
How are you, Jorge Salcedo?

270
00:28:26,455 --> 00:28:30,042
Go help your kids pack
