271
00:28:30,167 --> 00:28:31,961
Yeah.

272
00:28:37,258 --> 00:28:40,469
I know about Fredy Moya.
It's none of my business.

273
00:28:40,594 --> 00:28:44,265
- You're right. It's not your problem.
- You realise what happens if they find you?

274
00:28:45,808 --> 00:28:47,643
And your kids?

275
00:28:52,857 --> 00:28:56,902
I have to say goodbye to him.
We're in love. I can't leave like that.

276
00:28:57,027 --> 00:29:00,239
Mrs. Pallomari, if you stay, you die.

277
00:29:01,490 --> 00:29:02,700
Understood?

278
