464
00:44:24,579 --> 00:44:28,500
'All out of favours
and unlikely to find more,

465
00:44:28,625 --> 00:44:32,629
'they will spend the rest of their lives
in a U.S. prison.

466
00:44:32,754 --> 00:44:35,590
'The good guys didn't do much better.

467
00:44:35,715 --> 00:44:39,386
'Back in Colombia, Jorge Salcedo
