468
00:44:39,511 --> 00:44:42,889
The danger that he put himself in
to insure the success of our operation...

469
00:44:43,014 --> 00:44:47,185
'And in the States, despite testimony
that he was instrumental to our efforts

470
00:44:47,310 --> 00:44:50,855
'to capture and prosecute
the Cali godfathers,

471
00:44:50,980 --> 00:44:54,859
'he still had to plead guilty
