472
00:44:56,194 --> 00:44:58,405
'And from there, Jorge Salcedo...

473
00:44:59,614 --> 00:45:03,660
'...the guy who had the most to do
with bringing down the Cali cartel

474
00:45:03,785 --> 00:45:07,497
'disappeared into the Federal
Witness Protection Program

475
00:45:07,622 --> 00:45:10,291
'somewhere in the U.S.

476
00:45:11,751 --> 00:45:13,962
'A prison of its own.'

477
00:45:31,396 --> 00:45:35,817
- You knew him, right? Agent Camarena?
