00:45:35,942 --> 00:45:37,861
My first assignment out of the academy

479
00:45:37,986 --> 00:45:40,113
was a task force that
searched for him in Guadalajara.

480
00:45:42,115 --> 00:45:46,453
It all started there. Before him,
we didn't even know we were in a war.

481
00:45:47,662 --> 00:45:49,664
Another hot one down there
for you, huh?

482
00:45:49,789 --> 00:45:51,916
You took down the big players
