of what Medellín and Cali were.

487
00:46:08,349 --> 00:46:12,353
And now it's time to take the fight
to the real enemy in The War on Drugs.

488
00:46:12,479 --> 00:46:14,272
Mexico.

489
00:46:15,315 --> 00:46:17,066
"The real enemy"?

490
00:46:17,859 --> 00:46:21,863
Let me put in some calls. I'll make
this bullshit resignation go away.

491
00:46:24,824 --> 00:46:27,202
What else is a guy like you gonna do?

492
00:46:58,358 --> 00:47:01,194
All right, fellas. Let's move.
Keep going.

493
00:47:03,154 --> 00:47:04,989
Keep going.

494
00:47:47,156 --> 00:47:49,909
