496
00:47:54,998 --> 00:47:56,875
Stubborn.

497
00:48:00,628 --> 00:48:04,299
You can stand here
for an hour and count 20 of 'em going by.

498
00:48:04,424 --> 00:48:09,387
So... do you have to fix
the fence every time a storm hits?

499
00:48:11,097 --> 00:48:15,393
Someone has to do it.
That's how life works.

500
00:48:22,525 --> 00:48:25,987
You thinking
of taking them up on it? Mexico?

501
00:48:28,156 --> 00:48:29,991
It's different there.

502
00:48:31,034 --> 00:48:33,119
- Son, let me tell you...
- Dad.

503
00:48:35,496 --> 00:48:37,332
I've done enough.

504
00:48:39,918 --> 00:48:41,753
I'm through.

505
00:48:49,302 --> 00:48:51,262
Hand me that cutter.